metadata.description: Don't lie anymore, I have seen you, it was me who saw you with those torn eyes of mine. It's too late, you will be with me in this pit. You and I will become us. Scream as much as you want, It is so big here that the sound is not heard. No one sees or touches another. It is so small that there is only room for one body. Every body is placed diagonally in it. If it is big, it should be folded. A medium body width groove. You will be with me, you and I will become us.
